      <div class="cta-content">
        <h3>Not sure which service you need?</h3>
        <p>Book a free 30-minute consultation and we'll create a custom strategy for your business.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-consult">
          <span>Schedule Free Consultation</span>
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
            <path d="M4 10h12m-6-6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
